Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴  我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大小姐  请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期开始就这么忧郁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  心跳得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要一个人承受的哦  昴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  与次郎同学有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说被问到「今天的内衣是什么样的？」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有烦恼的话要说哦
